        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>Voss fuel line connectors are utilized on the HPV models. These connectors make it easy to connect
                    and disconnect fuel lines. Original installation of these new connectors onto a fuel hose is
                    normally done with special tools, but installation can be done in the field using readily available
                    shop tools.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
